    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1894-08-16T23:59:59-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1894-08-16T00:00:00-05:00" n="92" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d92">
                <head>No. 92.<lb/>
                    <hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Gresham</persName>
                            to Mr. <persName type="to">Baker</persName>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1894-08-16">
                            <hi rend="italic">August 16,
                            1894</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Your dispatch, 344, received. Pull advices from naval commanders show that
                        very few American citizens were concerned in the recent movement at
                        Bluefields, and none of good repute.</p>
            </div>
